title: PyCon Lithuania 2024 Promo

PyCon Lithuania 2024 is a conference focusing on Data, Web & More, that will have more than 60 sessions and more than 600 attendees. Featuring keynotes by PyDanny, Ritchie Vink, Arjan Codes, Robert Smallshire and Tom Christie.

For more information visit https://pycon.lt/2024
